Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:06.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,衰弱 贫困 贫富差距变大…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:08.35,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,黑暗时代的日本!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:10.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这个看不到未来的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:13.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,女神们降临了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:23.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,用可爱的笑容和歌声 改变这无可救药的日本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:26.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她们就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:30.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶像议员!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:34.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,星叶夏月议员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:36.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我来发言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:41.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,各位 饭团的话还是盐饭团好 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:43.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这不对啊!梅子饭团才好!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:45.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,女主角党扯什么淡啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:47.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,说到饭团的话当然是鳕鱼子了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:49.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不不不 绝对是海带泥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是金枪鱼蛋黄酱才对!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:53.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没想到会把这孩子养成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:57.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,滚回去!滚回去!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:00.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为什么 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.36,0:01:03.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,呀!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:07.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,呀啦啦 终于醒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:11.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,居然在学习会上睡着 真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:13.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,抱歉 差点睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:17.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,差点睡着?你那叫熟睡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:20.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:25.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个…刚刚在说什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:27.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,美谷村的垃圾问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:31.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,当地住民也反应给了女主角党以外的党派
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:34.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是解决起来还是很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:37.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,垃圾什么的收拾一下不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:38.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,谁来收拾?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:39.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,预算呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,收拾好的垃圾丢哪里去?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:44.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:49.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,也就是说你什么都没想过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢夏月的这种地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:58.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那么接下来去视察了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:42.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好棒 总觉得心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:45.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,变得不太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,虽说全国的主题公园的垃圾都被运到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不过这比预想的还严重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,能不能用法律规定一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:04.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,很遗憾 这没有违反这个村子的条例
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不要再丢来垃圾了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:10.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不要丢了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.80,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,保护美丽的自然环境!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:13.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.80,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,唉 熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她们是赞来党的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那么同是偶像议员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:23.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,NO.2 龙石堂千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:29.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我才不知道什么偶像议员 适可而止点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:33.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,再妨碍我工作的话 有你们好受的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有种你试试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,反对暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:41.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,再不适可而止点我们就叫消防车了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:43.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,警车才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:44.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,废话少说 给我让开!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:50.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,各位点到为止 火气别那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,古里议员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:55.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你也是这个村子出生的人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:57.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为什么对这种暴行不管不问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:02.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,暴行?这话就奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:07.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这里是我从先祖手上接管的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:09.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在自己的土地上干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:12.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,和各位没什么关系对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:16.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是 因为丢弃在这里的垃圾 村子的环境…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:21.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,只有有人活着 就无法避免产生垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:25.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我可是自己承担了这些垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:35.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还是说 这个村子产生的垃圾推给别处就好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:40.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那才叫自我放纵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:43.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我可没做任何违反法律的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:46.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,洗洗脸 明白了再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:52.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,千夏 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还是告诉瑞希姐比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:58.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不能就这点小事就去劳烦瑞希姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:03.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这个村子是我的故乡 这是需要我解决的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:06.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:08.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:22.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你还真是还敢出现在我们面前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:25.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是不会原谅你的 静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:26.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:30.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是什么展开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个…刚刚那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,静和千夏之间发生过什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:42.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你很在意?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:44.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在意在意 超级在意!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:49.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有不少事 不少事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:04.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为身上的气场 你伤害了太多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:09.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你的气场是无法融入别人的一把双刃剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:26.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个…有谁在吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:33.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫妖!不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,千夏?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:41.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑 居然叫我猫妖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是的 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:48.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不过你这么晚在这里干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:49.80,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:51.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,打扫…是说打扫垃圾?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:55.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,放任不管的话就会越来越严重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:58.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,而且还会有不好的味道 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:00.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为什么要做到这个份上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:02.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这个村子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:08.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这里 是我长大的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:13.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,小时候 我经常在这里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这里就像天堂一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以我一定要保护这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:27.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:29.80,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:33.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我也明白千夏的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:35.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:36.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:40.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会借助静在的女主角党的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:41.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:45.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你想知道?因为那个女人背叛了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:49.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是 她是抛弃了我们赞来党的叛徒!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:56.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,议员 这真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:09:02.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您放心 垃圾的处理按之前的来就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:07.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是偶像议员太闹的话我们这里也…给您满上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:13.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,毕竟要让别的地方处理垃圾那也不是一笔小数目了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:19.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶像议员?那帮小丫头能干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:22.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您尽管放心交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:26.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,既然议员都这么说了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:31.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,背叛?千夏是这么说静的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:33.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:39.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,背叛吗 旁人看来确实是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是这样的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:46.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她是不想再伤害任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:47.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:52.80,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你也看到了 静作为偶像的实力已经很厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.35,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的 她很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:58.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 静因为她超群的气场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:09.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就这样 静破坏了很多人的偶像才能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:14.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以静才离开了赞来党
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:19.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没做任何解释 硬是背上了叛徒的恶名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:23.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那静一直一个人的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是不想伤害任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:28.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那就是静的特有温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:34.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,幸惠姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:38.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是静的拍档 所以没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:45.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:46.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:47.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:51.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你这种地方我最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:57.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:00.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,能帮帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:02.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:04.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你是叫夏月来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还在想什么齐心协力吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:12.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现在不阻止他们的话 这里的自然环境就会死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以 请助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:15.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,毫无犹豫?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样不好吧 千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:21.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,听听她怎么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:27.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是为了让村里的人露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,希望你能帮千夏她们一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.90,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请别带上我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,只要有我在 千夏是不会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:41.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,必须是有静的女主角党才行!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:47.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是鬼丸静的拍档!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:50.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我不管发生什么 都不会被击败
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:59.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你倒是说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:03.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我没有为过去的事道歉的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:06.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 希望你们能帮助夏月一把
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:10.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,千夏 一起干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:13.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这里不是千夏最重要的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就是啊 千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,知道了 都说到这个份上了我就傲娇的答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:25.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是我有条件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,静 和我一决雌雄!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:33.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,终于来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.90,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,之后要比的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶像蹦极三蹦对决哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:44.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,拿下这个悬崖就能红的传说中的蹦极跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,如果能赢下这场蹦极对决
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:50.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我就和你们女主角党合作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:55.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是如果胆怯的跳不出去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就要对瑞希姐道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,瑞希姐是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:02.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,赞来党党首 不动瑞希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:08.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,被称作传说中的偶像三日月神乐的重现 是顶级偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:13.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么样 有胆量接受这场比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:14.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,当然!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:21.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我从小就最喜欢高处了 非常有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:22.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:23.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,堂堂正正决一雌雄!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:30.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,明白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:33.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:39.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,判断偶像气量的蹦极对决
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:41.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:46.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为了赞来党 不 也是为了不动瑞希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:52.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就算下面有河 在这个高度还是会害怕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看吧 马上就脚软了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不过这是你自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:01.03,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶像的道路可没你想的那么简单…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:02.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.79,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这个超爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,居然跳下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.79,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,千夏 看你蹲在地方 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没事 看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:20.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,只要集中精神的话 我也能跳 能跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:31.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,虽然是新人还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:35.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不过从这里跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:39.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是需要有在一万观众面前站上舞台的胆量的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你有这个胆量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,又跳下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:46.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那孩子到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个…轮到千夏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我知道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:58.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看好了 什么才是真正的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,让我来教教你!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:09.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,难道千夏怕了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:12.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,如果失败了就要去陪祖先了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.90,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,才不是啊 只是在屏气凝神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看好了 我现在就跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是绝对不许推我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:22.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我要自己掌握时机 千万别推
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:25.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我再说一遍 绝对不许推…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:28.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以都说了不许推啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,刚刚原来是装的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:38.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶像蹦极最后的比拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,至今只有两个人从这个悬崖跳下去过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,传说中的偶像 三日月神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:50.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还有我赞来党党首 不动瑞希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:55.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么样?怕了现在退出也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,和之前的完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:03.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真的好高 脚都有点软了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这次蹦极看来是跳不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:11.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,瑞希姐 你的传说现在就有我来继承吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:18.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我能听见 是观众们的欢呼声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看起来沉醉在自己的世界里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,成为像你一样的顶级偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这就是我报恩的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:35.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,瑞希姐 我现在就要起飞成为明星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:38.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:41.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:42.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,千夏!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:50.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,千夏!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:52.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:54.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:55.87,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不要勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她这么说了 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我想退出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这么高好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:06.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:11.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为在这里放弃的话 就没法和千夏她们合作了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:17.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我想要大家齐心协力 还原这个村子的环境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:20.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:24.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我能站在这里多亏了静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:31.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:33.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,加油了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,刚刚的声音是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:51.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,对不起 瑞希姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:57.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我没能成为你那样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好像断掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:10.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,辛亏下面有河
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月真幸运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哪里幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:20.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那件事该怎么办!虽然有赞来党的合作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:22.54,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,打算怎么拯救那个垃圾处理场?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看来是完全忘了正题了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:29.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不过掉下去的时候我想了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:33.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,虽然垃圾处理场看起来很脏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,总觉得像艺术品一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:43.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:46.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:48.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,以上!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:49.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:51.90,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,艺术品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:54.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,说不定这个点子可能有用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,议员 不好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:18:59.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,垃圾处理场…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 这个骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:20.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好像是偶像议员要美化丢在这儿的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:22.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,大家注意!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:27.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一件美化好的垃圾可以当一张握手券
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在美谷村这座垃圾丢弃场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:33.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,以偶像议员赞来党和女主角党为中心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:38.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,正在对丢弃的垃圾进行再生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:42.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在别人的土地上任意妄为!
